>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">810131702557</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD RUSH READY: This 18pc gold panning kit includes everything you need for collection, recovery and storage of gold! And, saving you time and effort, all the gold panning equipment included comes preassembled and ready to use right out of the box</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">UNIQUE SLUICE BOX: This gold panning kit from ASR Outdoor includes a compact aluminum 27 inch sluice box that enhances water capacity suspension through the entire channel, via a uniquely designed flared mouth; includes shoulder strap</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">5 GALLON BUCKET: Designed to work seamlessly with the included sifting screens, stack them on top of the bucket to create an effective material classification system that readies your pay dirt concentrate for gold panning or feeding a sluice box</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PROSPECTING TOOLS: This gold panning kit also includes a 16lb magnetic separator tool, 4oz snuffer bottles, x4 traditional gold pans, x3 classifier screens, 28 inch shovel, prospecting scoop, magnifying tweezers and glass storage vials</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 27 x 14 x 14 inches; Weight: 7.40lbs; Sluice Box Weight: 4.80lbs; Channel Width: 9.25 inches; Flare Width: 10.75 inches</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Complete Gold Prospecting Kit with 27\" Flared Aluminum Sluice Box</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">399.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Increase your gold recovery, while reducing river side set up time and effort with ASR Outdoor 27 Inch Flared Aluminum Sluice Box with 5 Gallon Bucket Complete Gold Panning Kit. With a uniquely designed, flared mouth gold sluice box and well curated assortment of prospecting tools, this gold panning kit has everything needed for collection, recovery and storage of gold.\n\nAnd, while the 27 inch folding sluice and 5 gallon bucket make this gold panning kit incredibly portable, the gold prospecting equipment we’ve included ensures you’re never compromising on the range of prospecting tools or processes needed for a successful day in the field. So, how is this kit going to cover end to end processing? Let’s start with the 5 gallon bucket and classifier screens (1/2, 1/8 and 1/12 inch included). \n\nThe 5 gallon bucket has been designed to work seamlessly with stackable sifting screens; when layered on top of the bucket, you’ve now created an effective classification system to remove unwanted material from your pay dirt concentrate. Use the uniquely sized and easily portable 28 inch shovel we've included to collect material for processing. But, before you start panning or sluicing with your classified pay dirt, use the 16lb magnetic separator pick up tool; this will help to remove black sand and any other heavy magnetic materials from your classified pay dirt, making it easier to extract gold.\n\nWhether you choose to feed your river sluice or work on gold panning techniques, you’ve got both options with this kit! With a uniquely designed flared mouth opening, the design of this 27 inch fixed gold sluice box will allow more water capacity suspension to flow through the entire channel of the sluice box. The sluice box comes with preinstalled rubber matting, carpet, miners moss, angled aluminum mesh and large 18 gauge zinc plated steel riffles to help trap gold. And, weighing in at just 4.80lbs, this gold sluice box is compact and lightweight, making it easy to trek your claim site. Alternatively, the traditional finishing gold pans included measure 10 and 14 inches, are molded from one piece of high impact ABS plastic, rust resistant and buoyant in water, ideal for fine gold recovery and can handle large amounts of material.\n\nIf you’re lucky enough to spot gold, you can use the included snuffer bottles to extract gold flakes or nuggets and store them in the screw top glass vials for safe keeping. If not, well, we’re sorry to say, it’s back to the bucket. All the components of this gold panning kit come pre-assembled and ready to use right out of the box, making it gold rush ready! No tools required. Good luck out there!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
